#

Herb-Crusted Salmon with Citrus Salsa

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

HealthyQuickDinner

Description

A flavorful and healthy salmon dish topped with a refreshing citrus salsa, perfect for a quick dinner!

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • fresh parsley, chopped: 2 tbsp
  • fresh dill, chopped: 2 tbsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • orange, diced: 1
  • grapefruit, diced: 1
  • red onion, finely chopped: 1/4
  • lime juice: 2 tbsp
